title: Vintage & Spacious One-Bedroom at The Historic Grand Apartments
posting_body: ['Property Address', '1962 Grand Ave - 205 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Available 10/1: Back corner one-bedroom in the heart of Grand Ave!', 'This spacious second-floor apartment home has rustic hardwood floors throughout and original built-in cabinets in the kitchen.', "You'll have access to huge closets and a large, open living room.", 'Updated windows bring in plenty of natural sunlight to warm up your new home!', 'Situated between the University of St. Thomas and Macalester College, the Historic Grand Apartments are in an exciting, centralized location.', 'There are many local shops and restaurants within walking distance or you can catch the bus for convenient commuting into downtown.', 'Spacious layouts, historic charm, restored hardwood floors, and gorgeous built-ins make historic living unbeatable!', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Secured Entry', 'Historic Building', 'Hardwood floors', 'Heat Water Trash Paid', '24/7 Emergency Maintenance', 'New Windows', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 750', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,024.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
